## 🌟 About Me

Hello! I'm **Arpit Tagade** — a full‑stack engineer who loves blending
software, artificial intelligence and IoT hardware into polished user experiences.
My background spans
Next.js, Spring Boot, Node.js and Arduino/ESP32 platforms, and I get excited
when cloud services and edge devices work together seamlessly.

Here’s a snapshot of what I do and value:

- 🎨 **Design matters:** clean interfaces paired with robust backend logic.
- 🧠 **AI everywhere:** from chatbots to intelligent agents; I push LLMs beyond
  simple question‑answering.
- 🛠️ **Hardware hacking:** bringing generative AI and robotics together for
  real‑world tasks.
- ✨ **Curiosity first:** exploring new ideas like agentic AI, multi‑modal
  orchestration and RAG pipelines keeps me motivated.
- 🤝 **Community:** learning in public and collaborating with fellow builders is
  my favourite way to grow.

> **TL;DR:** I engineer delightful solutions where AI meets hardware. 🧠⚙️

